<li>To <strong>verify RSpec</strong>: type this into your console:
  <pre class="code">> rspec</pre>

  You should see something like:
  <pre class="code">
No examples found.

Finished in 0.00022 seconds (files took 0.06779 seconds to load)
0 examples, 0 failures            
  </pre>
  
  <p class="italic"> Don't freak out if there are some pending tests!</p>
  <p>If you have generated a scaffold (or any controller/model), it generated an empty spec file - which might contain some pending specs. </p>
  <p>This is actually great news - RSpec is working as intended!</p>
</li>
